Package: sequenza
Title:   Analysis and visualization of tumor sequencing data.
Description: This package provides tools to analyze NGS data, including cellularity and ploidy estimation, mutation and copy number detection and quantification, detection of mono-allelic expression and allelic/subclonal mutation classification.
Version: 0.0.7
Date: 2013-06-24
Author: Francesco Favero
Maintainer: Francesco Favero <favero@cbs.dtu.dk>
Depends: R (>= 2.15.1), beeswarm, copynumber, parallel, squash
Suggests: 
License: GPL-2
